 Svako jutro se budio

89
00:08:32,160 --> 00:08:35,580
 Meditirao i u sebi ponavljao

90
00:08:35,580 --> 00:08:38,240
 Budi dobar, budi ok, širi ljubav

91
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,720
 Širi svima

92
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:44,080
 Šalji ljubav izvoru, suncu, mjesecu

93
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:47,780
 Svim ljudima, bez obzira jesu li dobri, jesu li loši

94
00:08:47,780 --> 00:08:50,000
 Biljkama, životinjama

95
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,460
 Svako jutro

96
00:08:51,460 --> 00:08:53,340
 I stalno sam u glavi to ponavljao

97
00:08:53,340 --> 00:08:55,720
 Budi ok, budi ok, budi ok

98
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:58,580
 Jer ja sam prolazio jednu svoju transformaciju

99
