 Nisam ja od uvijek bio ovakav

100
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:01,860
 Ljudi koji mene znaju

101
00:09:01,860 --> 00:09:04,040
 Dugo godina, oni

102
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:06,680
 Danas se čude

103
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:08,760
 Toj mojoj transformaciji

104
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:10,420
 Vi sada, svi koji mene gledate

105
00:09:10,420 --> 00:09:13,240
 Ja sam jedan potpuno drugi lik

106
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:15,520
 Ja sam lik koji je

107
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:17,580
 Odrstao u kozari boku

108
00:09:17,580 --> 00:09:20,240
 Ja sam odrstao na tribini

109
