 Znači ja sam 20 godina

110
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,760
 Gotovo svaki vikend

111
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:26,580
 Tek me ludilo

112
00:09:26,580 --> 00:09:28,960
 Kvart, da ne pričam kakav je bio

113
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,620
 I tako dalje

114
00:09:29,620 --> 00:09:30,260
 I tako dalje

115
00:09:30,260 --> 00:09:32,320
 A sam djete ulice

116
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:35,620
 Piše i na najci

117
00:09:35,620 --> 00:09:37,320
 Da, da, nije slučajno

118
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:41,320
 Ja sam odrasto na ulici

119
00:09:41,320 --> 00:09:43,200
 I sigurno

120
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:46,200
 A kad sam ja bio mlađi

121
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,020
 Nisam ja

122
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:48,320
 Tad mogo doću kvart

123
