 Znaš, smijanja, otpora

132
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:02,960
 I tako dalje

133
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,620
 I tako dalje

134
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:05,120
 Ali

135
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,760
 Taj jedan

136
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:10,220
 Nadnaravan rad

137
00:10:10,220 --> 00:10:12,220
 Na samom sebi

138
