 Evo, te dvije i osme je krenuo nekakav moj put

166
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:14,640
 I radio sam i sa gospođom Mirjanom

167
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:20,160
 I išao sam dugo godina kod mog danas prijatelja

168
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:24,000
 Mirse Dervišana Bjelašnicu čuvat ovce

169
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:26,720
 Svi su mi se smijali

170
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:30,880
 Ali prvi put kad sam otišao tamo

171
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:33,600
 Spoznao sam da je to nešto potpuno drugačije

172
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,440
 Da mi to treba

173
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:40,200
 Radio sam i na mnogim tima

174
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:42,720
 Ajmo ih tako nazvat nekako duhovnim aspektima

175
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:46,300
 Majstor sam učitelj reikija

176
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:48,440
 Bio sam jedno vrijeme i u tom smjeru

177
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:52,560
 Iniciran sam u drugi stupanj inka šamanizma

178
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:55,240
 Tako da sam išao i u tom smjeru

179
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:57,560
 Kroz cijelu tu priču

180
00:12:57,560 --> 00:13:00,320
 Naravno da sam puno radio na sebi

181
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,120
 I kroz Mirelu

182
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:05,200
 Ipak je ona, ljubav mog života

183
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:08,400
 Moja partnerica s kojom dijelim apsolutno sve

184
00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:10,100
 I imam djecu

185
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:11,440
 Mirela igra

186
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:13,880
 Vrlo bitnu ulogu u mom životu

187
00:13:13,880 --> 00:13:14,680
 Vrlo bitnu

188
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:16,220
 Ona je tu puno puta

189
00:13:16,220 --> 00:13:19,540
 Ta jedan balans koji meni treba

190
00:13:19,540 --> 00:13:21,560
 Kako ja njoj, tako i ona meni

191
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:25,740
 I kroz cijeli taj

192
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:27,740
 Sad sam malo ti isprepleo

193
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:30,000
 Duhovnost i rad na sebi

194
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:32,120
 I kroz sve te godine

195
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:35,620
 Nekako sam sve više upoznavao sebe

196
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:37,120
 Mijenjao se

197
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:39,800
 Mislim da je tako

198
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:41,600
 Kod svakog

199
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:44,500
 Ko krene na taj jedan put promjene

200
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:46,460
 I rada na sebi

201
00:13:46,460 --> 00:13:49,560
 Da počne sve više upoznava sebe

202
00:13:49,560 --> 00:13:54,740
 Ko je on, što želi, gdje ide, zbog čega ide u tom smjeru

203
00:13:54,740 --> 00:13:57,440
 Šta se promijenilo od onog trenutka

204
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,520
